{
  "total_duration": 474.756,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 7.96,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你有没有遇到过这种时刻：手机没信号、家里 Wi-Fi 断了、班级通知发错群，或者游戏语音突然坏掉？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 8.31,
      "end": 13.35,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这时候真正重要的不是手机本身，而是：消息到底能不能送到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 13.7,
      "end": 33.74,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的故事很老派，但想法很现代。Mr. James Scott 的新车库装不了电话，他没有一直等，而是用十二只鸽子搭了一个自己的备用通信系统。更妙的是，故事最后会悄悄点题：这种方法看上去落后，却有一个电话做不到的优点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 34.09,
      "end": 53.993,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始，Mr. James Scott 已经有一个车库，在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Silbury"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。现在他又在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pinhurst"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "买了另一个车库。两个地方不远，但只要有两个车库，就会有很多事情要互相通知：零件、维修、客人、紧急情况。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 54.343,
      "end": 71.527,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "问题来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pinhurst is only five miles from Silbury"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，Pinhurst 离 Silbury 只有五英里。可是 Mr. Scott"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cannot get a telephone for his new garage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里不是说他不会接电话，而是他的新车库没办法装上电话服务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 71.877,
      "end": 94.288,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以他的办法很奇怪，也很有效：他买了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "twelve pigeons"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，十二只鸽子。昨天，一只鸽子"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "carried the first message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把第一条消息从 Pinhurst 带到了 Silbury。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The bird covered the distance in three minutes."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它三分钟就飞完了这段距离。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 94.638,
      "end": 129.458,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是一次好玩的表演，而是真的用起来了。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Up to now, Mr. Scott has sent a great many requests for spare parts and other urgent messages"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。到现在为止，他已经发了很多索取备件的请求，还有别的紧急消息。最后，叙述者开了个小玩笑：他已经开始了自己的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "private telephone service"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，私人“电话”服务。题目"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Wrong Numbers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的幽默就在这里：鸽子很旧，可它根本不拨号码，所以就不会拨错号码。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 129.807,
      "end": 144.679,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课表面上有鸽子，但重点不是动物知识。它真正好笑、也真正聪明的地方，是最后那一下点题：不用电话，反而没有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wrong numbers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不会拨错号码。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 145.029,
      "end": 151.958,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就像现在手机没信号的时候，换一个 App、借朋友手机、打固定电话，或者直接写纸条？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 152.308,
      "end": 169.932,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。今天我们说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "backup communication"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，备用通信。Mr. Scott 那个年代，新车库没有电话，就像现在你在地下车库、山里、机场、学校大楼里突然没有信号。正常系统靠不住，他就自己造了一个能工作的系统。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 170.282,
      "end": 176.799,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那标题"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Wrong Numbers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？不是“没有错号”吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 177.149,
      "end": 195.429,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "字面上是“不会有拨错号码”。普通电话很现代，但可能拨错号、接错线、找错人。鸽子听起来落后，可它只在两个固定车库之间飞，路线清清楚楚。它不像电话，却避开了电话最尴尬的问题：拨错号码。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 195.779,
      "end": 205.252,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这篇故事最后不是单纯夸鸽子，而是在开一个聪明的小玩笑：旧办法居然解决了新工具会犯的错。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 205.602,
      "end": 234.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正是这样。标题"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Wrong Numbers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是一开始就解释完的，它是读到最后才亮起来的笑点。再看几个关键词。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是只指手机短信，而是任何要传递的信息。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "covered the distance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cover"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“盖住”，而是“走完、飞完一段距离”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent messages"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是必须尽快到达的紧急消息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 235.191,
      "end": 240.678,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Up to now"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 241.027,
      "end": 264.375,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是今天的语法线索。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday, a pigeon carried the first message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这是昨天发生的一次测试事件。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Up to now, Mr. Scott has sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，是从那以后一直到现在，已经发过很多次。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he has begun his own private telephone service"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，说明结果已经出现：这个私人系统真的开始运转了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 264.725,
      "end": 270.533,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mr. James Scott has a garage in Silbury and now he has just bought another garage in Pinhurst."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 270.883,
      "end": 279.019,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pinhurst is only five miles from Silbury, but Mr. Scott cannot get a telephone for his new garage, so he has just bought twelve pigeons."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 279.369,
      "end": 284.265,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday, a pigeon carried the first message from Pinhurst to Silbury."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 284.614,
      "end": 287.782,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The bird covered the distance in three minutes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 288.132,
      "end": 295.476,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Up to now, Mr. Scott has sent a great many requests for spare parts and other urgent messages from one garage to the other."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 295.826,
      "end": 300.05,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In this way, he has begun his own private 'telephone' service."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 300.4,
      "end": 303.16,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "message"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 303.51,
      "end": 305.118,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "message"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 305.468,
      "end": 326.491,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "message"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“消息、信息”。它不只等于手机短信。纸条、口信、邮件、班级通知，都可以是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文里说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "carried the first message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是把第一条信息送到了另一个车库。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 326.841,
      "end": 329.641,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "distance"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "distance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 329.991,
      "end": 331.719,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "distance"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "distance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 332.069,
      "end": 350.268,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "distance"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "distance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“距离”。课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The bird covered the distance in three minutes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "covered"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“盖住”，而是“走完、飞完”。所以整句是：这只鸟三分钟飞完了这段距离。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 350.618,
      "end": 353.37,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "urgent"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 353.72,
      "end": 355.328,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "urgent"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 355.678,
      "end": 373.526,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "urgent"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是“紧急的、急迫的”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent messages"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是需要尽快送到的紧急消息。比如会议时间改了、零件马上要用、家人需要你立刻回复，这些都可以叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "urgent messages"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 373.876,
      "end": 414.363,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的语法不要背成表格，放回故事里看。第一句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday, a pigeon carried the first message"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，用的是过去的一次动作：昨天，第一条消息送到了。后面"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Up to now, Mr. Scott has sent a great many requests"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，重点变成“到现在为止已经做了很多次”。最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he has begun his own private telephone service"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是只说开始那一下，而是说现在结果已经成立：他有了一个自己的通信服务。记住这条故事逻辑：过去发生的一次成功测试，慢慢变成了现在还在用的系统。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 414.713,
      "end": 432.193,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天这个“备用通信方案”放进你自己的生活。下面有三个现代场景：没信号、发错群、紧急通知。你从 word bank 里选短语，把三个空都补上。重点不是鸽子，而是消息怎样可靠地送到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 432.543,
      "end": 443.767,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老师有一次在地下停车场完全没有信号，只好借朋友的手机发消息。那一刻我突然觉得："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A good message needs a good way to travel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 444.117,
      "end": 474.756,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：第一步听课文全文，第二步点核心句的原音，第三步录自己读一遍，第四步看一句小反馈、再试一次。读顺以后，再做 ① 生活场景，把备用通信放进你自己的故事里；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。加油、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "you can do it"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "！"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
